<h2 id="write-off-an-invoice-from-the-open-customers-invoices-page" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-write-off-journal-customer.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Write off an invoice from the Open customers invoices page</h2>
