<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-write-off-journal-customer.md" sourcestartlinenumber="74">On the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-write-off-journal-customer.md" sourcestartlinenumber="74">Action Pane</strong>, click <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/create-write-off-journal-customer.md" sourcestartlinenumber="74">Invoice</strong>.</li>
